  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2342690/extras/fd403c1e5c3b39dc4970f2a29f1fccc8.avif?t=1744553284\" width=616 height=250 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >🧋A relaxing game set in a cozy town</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In this game, players returned to a charming little town where they become the savior of a struggling boba tea shop. With your help, the owner of the shop will be able to make the best boba tea in town and attract customers from all over!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2342690/extras/1cb44a0f6e5280f68d6ddfdb45df0c57.poster.avif?t=1744553284\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2342690/extras/1cb44a0f6e5280f68d6ddfdb45df0c57.webm?t=1744553284\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2342690/extras/1cb44a0f6e5280f68d6ddfdb45df0c57.mp4?t=1744553284\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2342690/extras/8e352efec24465483ca5c7cf18ba1ad2.poster.avif?t=1744553284\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2342690/extras/8e352efec24465483ca5c7cf18ba1ad2.webm?t=1744553284\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2342690/extras/8e352efec24465483ca5c7cf18ba1ad2.mp4?t=1744553284\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >🧋Use boba milk Tea ingredients to fight</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >But that's not all, as the sun sets in the small town, a mysterious and dangerous world awakens. Using your trusty boba tea weapons, known as Bobas, you will defeat enemies and gain new inspiration for your boba tea creations.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2342690/extras/ee6d91195eb2d2fbb04f5f73b810f44a.poster.avif?t=1744553284\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2342690/extras/ee6d91195eb2d2fbb04f5f73b810f44a.webm?t=1744553284\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2342690/extras/ee6d91195eb2d2fbb04f5f73b810f44a.mp4?t=1744553284\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >🧋Play at your own pace</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >As you progress through the game, you will also have the chance to develop relationships with various NPCs, possibly even falling in love with them. The game's storyline is enriched by a variety of town tasks, mini-games, and exciting fishing quests that will keep you engaged and entertained for hours.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2342690/extras/46ba71fff402796350772af1b573a467.poster.avif?t=1744553284\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2342690/extras/46ba71fff402796350772af1b573a467.webm?t=1744553284\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2342690/extras/46ba71fff402796350772af1b573a467.mp4?t=1744553284\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2342690/extras/bbd47c18e4a9a1fcd173dfcf67a58e0f.poster.avif?t=1744553284\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2342690/extras/bbd47c18e4a9a1fcd173dfcf67a58e0f.webm?t=1744553284\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2342690/extras/bbd47c18e4a9a1fcd173dfcf67a58e0f.mp4?t=1744553284\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2342690/extras/fd403c1e5c3b39dc4970f2a29f1fccc8.avif?t=1744553284\" width=616 height=250 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >🧋A relaxing game set in a cozy town</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In this game, players returned to a charming little town where they become the savior of a struggling boba tea shop. With your help, the owner of the shop will be able to make the best boba tea in town and attract customers from all over!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2342690/extras/1cb44a0f6e5280f68d6ddfdb45df0c57.poster.avif?t=1744553284\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2342690/extras/1cb44a0f6e5280f68d6ddfdb45df0c57.webm?t=1744553284\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2342690/extras/1cb44a0f6e5280f68d6ddfdb45df0c57.mp4?t=1744553284\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2342690/extras/8e352efec24465483ca5c7cf18ba1ad2.poster.avif?t=1744553284\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2342690/extras/8e352efec24465483ca5c7cf18ba1ad2.webm?t=1744553284\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2342690/extras/8e352efec24465483ca5c7cf18ba1ad2.mp4?t=1744553284\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >🧋Use boba milk Tea ingredients to fight</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >But that's not all, as the sun sets in the small town, a mysterious and dangerous world awakens. Using your trusty boba tea weapons, known as Bobas, you will defeat enemies and gain new inspiration for your boba tea creations.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2342690/extras/ee6d91195eb2d2fbb04f5f73b810f44a.poster.avif?t=1744553284\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2342690/extras/ee6d91195eb2d2fbb04f5f73b810f44a.webm?t=1744553284\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2342690/extras/ee6d91195eb2d2fbb04f5f73b810f44a.mp4?t=1744553284\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >🧋Play at your own pace</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >As you progress through the game, you will also have the chance to develop relationships with various NPCs, possibly even falling in love with them. The game's storyline is enriched by a variety of town tasks, mini-games, and exciting fishing quests that will keep you engaged and entertained for hours.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2342690/extras/46ba71fff402796350772af1b573a467.poster.avif?t=1744553284\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2342690/extras/46ba71fff402796350772af1b573a467.webm?t=1744553284\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2342690/extras/46ba71fff402796350772af1b573a467.mp4?t=1744553284\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2342690/extras/bbd47c18e4a9a1fcd173dfcf67a58e0f.poster.avif?t=1744553284\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2342690/extras/bbd47c18e4a9a1fcd173dfcf67a58e0f.webm?t=1744553284\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2342690/extras/bbd47c18e4a9a1fcd173dfcf67a58e0f.mp4?t=1744553284\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
